OL,3,CMan suffers third-degree burns after
OL,4,Cvape explodes in his pocket
OL,6,FHe has now issued a warning to those
OL,7,Fwho vape, saying they are "potentially
OL,8,Fwalking around with a ticking time
OL,9,Fbomb in their pocket".
OL,11,FGraphic images show the extent of Mr
OL,12,FKane's injuries. He later sued the
OL,13,Fvape shop where he bought the e-
OL,14,Fcigarette, winning more than #20,000
OL,15,Fin compensation.
OL,17,FMr Kane was shopping with his daughter
OL,18,Fwhen he says his jeans "started
OL,19,Ffizzing and sparking like a firework".
