OL,3,CMan suffers third-degree burns after
OL,4,Cvape explodes in his pocket
OL,6,F"People need to know how dangerous e-
OL,7,Fcigarettes are," he said. "It all
OL,8,Fhappened in a flash. The pain was
OL,9,Fincredible - like my leg had been put
OL,10,Fin an oven.
OL,12,F"I went to a vape shop as e-cigs were
OL,13,Fsupposed to be healthier, but instead
OL,14,Fthey scarred me for life.
OL,16,F"Now I tell anyone vaping is not worth
OL,17,Fit. They are potentially walking
OL,18,Faround with a ticking time bomb in
OL,19,Ftheir pocket.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
