OL,3,CMan suffers third-degree burns after
OL,4,Cvape explodes in his pocket
OL,6,F"I got third degree burns in seconds
OL,7,Ffrom a battery and have the scars to
OL,8,Fprove it."
OL,10,FRobert took up vaping in April 2019
OL,11,Fafter government advice promoting it
OL,12,Fas healthier than smoking.
OL,14,FHe alleged he was not given safety
OL,15,Fadvice on how to store his e-cigarette
OL,16,For batteries when he bought it from a
OL,17,Fshop.
OL,19,FRecalling the explosion, he added: "It
OL,20,Fwas the same sound as when you first
OL,21,Flight a firework.
