OL,3,CMan suffers third-degree burns after
OL,4,Cvape explodes in his pocket
OL,6,F"And then I had this incredible
OL,7,Fburning pain on my leg. I saw some
OL,8,Fsmoke there was some sparks and a
OL,9,Fsecond bang."
OL,11,FThe charred remains of the battery
OL,12,Ffell to the floor, which he later
OL,13,Frecovered.
OL,15,FHis sister rushed him to Wythenshawe
OL,16,FHospital, where he said he was given a
OL,17,Fwarm water shower to remove the
OL,18,Fbattery acid.
