OL,3,CMan suffers third-degree burns after
OL,4,Cvape explodes in his pocket
OL,6,FThe engineering technician, from
OL,7,FWythenshawe, said medics told him the
OL,8,Facid had eaten through three layers of
OL,9,Fskin and was one of the worst injuries
OL,10,Fthey had seen.
OL,12,FHe added: "It was horrific, like I had
OL,13,Fbeen in a fireball. The nurses were
OL,14,Fpeeling off my skin.
OL,16,F"It had burnt so deep you could see my
OL,17,Fmuscle. It was 11 out of 10 pain -
OL,18,Findescribable."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
