OL,3,CMan suffers third-degree burns after
OL,4,Cvape explodes in his pocket
OL,6,FHe spent 12 days in a burns unit,
OL,7,Freceiving morphine and antibiotics and
OL,8,Fhad to learn to walk again.
OL,10,F"That was one of the hardest things,
OL,11,Fhaving to learn to walk again along
OL,12,Fwith the constant pain in my leg,
OL,13,Fwhich felt like it was constantly on
OL,14,Ffire," he added.
OL,16,FCatherine Citron, a personal injury
OL,17,Fspecialist from Express Solicitors who
OL,18,Fwon him compensation, said: "Robert
OL,19,Fwas trying to be healthier by not
OL,20,Fsmoking tobacco and now has been left
OL,21,Fwith a badly scarred leg for life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
