OL,6,F"His injuries were horrific and not
OL,7,Fwhat you expect to happen from a shop
OL,8,Fbought e cigarette battery.
OL,10,F"Any premises selling e-cigarettes or
OL,11,Fvapes need to give appropriate safety
OL,12,Fadvice."
